<plot>A beautiful, rich pianist who gets stuck on her way to a concert has to get on a bus for the first time in her life, only to find out that across from her sits a potential suicide bomber. In her growing panic, she decides to move to a safer seat - next to Yuri - a drunk, bitter and tired Russian soldier with a gun on his lap. Inspired by true events, Just In Case is a five minute impossible love story which takes place in an impossible reality.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?282658</url></doc>
